task.summary: Added grbl printout while in development mode.
Now writes user commands to tempCommand.txt.
Added additional logging for grbl responses to user commands.
Changed py commands to python. Let's hope the user doesn't have multiple versions of python installed.
Added virtual gcode tracer to bypass Arduino for testing.
Case of STL files no longer breaks Slic3r.
Upload button is now disabled while slicing.
Only allow one file upload for CNC machine.
Updated the look of the G-code tab.
Updates to the Rotation queue logic.
Added click and drag rotation for Model rendering.
Improved click and drag rotation for Model rendering.
Added g-code placeholder image in Model tab.
Adjusted model in rendering to correct position.
Fixed model positioning and Tracer freezing on second consecutive run.
Added config.ini file, updated minimum rotation degree to be a double.
Updated the max foam dimensions and travel distance for both machines.
Updated the GcodeTracer to work with real sized profiles.
Fixed error with percentage and time remaining calculations.
Truncates precision of commands for G0 as well.
Changes repositioning for hotwire to G0.
GcodeTracer now shows the location of the foam block, help html split into two files.
Centered Button Menu, updated rotation demo profiles.
Inverted y axis for keyboard controls on Hotwire machine.
